<h2 class="bold font-l">Trish's Last Words</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
If Cole uses his powers for Evil, Trish's last words are her voicing her disappointment in him. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="4ujspj" data-video-descrip="As Nazi lays there mortally wounded from the fight against the Horseshoe Centrist, he demands that Commie stop coddling him and kill the Radical Centrist to protect his people's heritage from &amp;quot;the Jews.&amp;quot;" data-video-title="Nazi really hates Centrists" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/4ujspj_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/4ujspj.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/DyingDeclarationOfHate" data-video-tropename="Dying Declaration of Hate" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="WebVideo/Jreg" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/4ujspj.jpg">
<p><span class="bold">Nazi really hat...</span></p>
</a>
